00:11:23.770 --> 00:11:25.240 align:middle line:90%
So how did you get programmed?

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:27.670 align:middle line:84%
Well, we all know
about inculturation.

00:11:27.670 --> 00:11:31.480 align:middle line:84%
