00:11:48.340 --> 00:11:51.700 align:middle line:84%
and we begin to build defense
mechanisms and defense

00:11:51.700 --> 00:11:52.640 align:middle line:90%
strategies.

00:11:52.640 --> 00:11:53.440 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:56.990 align:middle line:84%
