week and sit you back down,

00:12:42.460 --> 00:12:47.090 align:middle line:84%
because let's say I want to
move you toward conservatism.

00:12:47.090 --> 00:12:51.430 align:middle line:84%
And I'll put a jar of hand
sanitizer on the table.

00:12:51.430 --> 00:12:54.550 align:middle line:84%
You will see that
your hand sanitizer,

00:12:54.550 --> 00:12:57.610 align:middle line:84%
