Germs, danger-- beware.

00:13:07.790 --> 00:13:08.590 align:middle line:90%
Caution.

00:13:08.590 --> 00:13:09.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Of course.

00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:10.960 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Those are
the thought processes

00:13:10.960 --> 00:13:12.670 align:middle line:90%
