And you--

00:25:41.950 --> 00:25:42.810 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Isn't that
what life's for?

00:25:42.810 --> 00:25:45.420 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It is, and if you have
hypnosis or something to work

00:25:45.420 --> 00:25:46.620 align:middle line:90%
with, you could.

