00:26:26.704 --> 00:26:28.120 align:middle line:84%
you're not going
to be programmed,

00:26:28.120 --> 00:26:31.030 align:middle line:84%
and then how do you go about
choosing to educate yourself

00:26:31.030 --> 00:26:34.180 align:middle line:84%
on the affairs of the
