I'm not one that says
unplug from media.

00:26:42.910 --> 00:26:48.140 align:middle line:84%
Indeed, I spend a good deal of
time paying attention to media.

00:26:48.140 --> 00:26:49.780 align:middle line:90%
I'll give you an example.

00:26:49.780 --> 00:26:52.281 align:middle line:84%
One morning I'm
watching two networks.

00:26:52.281 --> 00:26:53.155 align:middle line:90%
One's a conservative.

00:26:53.155 --> 00:26:56.020 align:middle line:90%
The other's a liberal network.

00:26:56.020 --> 00:26:57.540 align:middle line:90%
They're having a poll.

