It's the same poll.

00:27:00.129 --> 00:27:02.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Each one is
skewing for their audience.

00:27:02.170 --> 00:27:02.590 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: We are
creatures that want

00:27:02.590 --> 00:27:04.360 align:middle line:90%
to hear what we want to hear.

00:27:04.360 --> 00:27:05.290 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:27:05.290 --> 00:27:08.470 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: We look for feedback
