00:27:08.470 --> 00:27:09.729 align:middle line:90%
So I happen to be liberal.

00:27:09.729 --> 00:27:11.020 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to listen to liberal.

00:27:11.020 --> 00:27:13.260 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going to go to Fox.

00:27:13.260 --> 00:27:14.920 align:middle line:84%
If I happen to be
conservative, I'm

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:18.150 align:middle line:90%
certainly not going to MSNBC.

00:27:18.150 --> 00:27:22.400 align:middle line:84%
So on this same
day on one network,

