00:27:26.020 --> 00:27:30.910 align:middle line:84%
forced to work two jobs in order
to pay for their children's

00:27:30.910 --> 00:27:33.710 align:middle line:84%
education and put them
in private schools,

00:27:33.710 --> 00:27:37.360 align:middle line:84%
since our public education
system is failing?"

