00:27:39.970 --> 00:27:43.780 align:middle line:84%
Should poor taxpayers be
forced to pay for rich kids

00:27:43.780 --> 00:27:46.000 align:middle line:90%
to go to private school?

00:27:46.000 --> 00:27:49.000 align:middle line:84%
Now the issue is
about school vouchers.

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:51.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Right, this is how
the network's positioned-- it's

00:27:51.500 --> 00:27:52.550 align:middle line:90%
how the media positions it.

00:27:52.550 --> 00:27:54.966 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Now I don't believe
